## Repo layout

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `lib/app/` | `router.dart` (GoRouter), `theme.dart`, `theme_settings.dart`, shared widgets (`app_bar_drawer_leading`, `notification_app_bar_action`, `theme_picker_sheet`) |
| `lib/core/` | `supabase_client.dart`, `constants.dart` (roles, `kTable*`, buckets), auth (`profile_role_notifier`, `auth_metadata`), services (`fcm_service`, `notification_edge_service`, `sms_service`), errors |
