| `lib/shared/models/` | Data models |
| `supabase/migrations/` | Postgres DDL + RLS |
| `supabase/functions/` | Edge (Deno): `send-notification`, `create-student`, etc. |
| `scripts/set-fcm-secret.ps1` | UTF-8 **no BOM** env file for `supabase secrets set` (Windows) |

